    </teiHeader> <text type="card"> <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs=""/>Hrn Dr. Pollak Adam,</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb62" type="place">Wien XII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1239" type="place">Meidlinger Hauptstr 56</rs>.</addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs=""/><date>9. X. 1916</date>.</dateline><salute>Verehrter Herr Doktor,</salute></opener><p>vielen Dank für Ihren Brief. Seit <date>30. Sept.</date> bin ich wieder daheim. Pa<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t es Ihnen, schon <date>Do<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>erstag (12.)</date> gegen <time><hi rend="underline" n="1">7</hi> Abends</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie mir willko<c rendition="#gemination-m"/>en!</p><closer>Herzlich grüßen<unclear>d</unclear><lb/>Ihr ergebner<lb/><signed>ArthurSchnitzler</signed></closer></div></body> </text></TEI>